four times as much just to say "hello."

685
00:42:33,237 --> 00:42:35,644
So it's the Shirks.
That's not so bad.

686
00:42:35,738 --> 00:42:37,649
Well, that's if they show up.

687
00:42:37,742 --> 00:42:40,657
Just because they showed up
to collect the money...

