745
00:46:40,898 --> 00:46:43,104
I know.

746
00:46:43,192 --> 00:46:46,276
- How do I look in this?
- Oh, beautiful.

747
00:46:46,361 --> 00:46:50,857
You look beautiful
in everything. Mm-hmm.

748
00:46:51,658 --> 00:46:54,065
Hi!

749
00:46:56,495 --> 00:46:58,404
Hi.

750
00:46:58,497 --> 00:47:00,122
