how long will the job take?

777
00:48:12,105 --> 00:48:14,014
Two weeks.

778
00:48:14,107 --> 00:48:16,016
Two weeks?
Two weeks?

779
00:48:16,109 --> 00:48:19,809
You sound like a parakeet.
"Two weeks? Two weeks?" [ Laughs ]

780
00:48:19,904 --> 00:48:22,940
Well, uh, two weeks.
It's... It's amazing.

781
00:48:23,032 --> 00:48:24,941
- Amazing, nothing.
