790
00:48:54,810 --> 00:48:57,727
Because I'm standing
in a pile of rubble...

791
00:48:57,813 --> 00:49:00,220
and we don't
have the permits to un-rubble it.

792
00:49:00,315 --> 00:49:03,898
"Exaggerating"? Honey, we're living
