793
00:49:03,985 --> 00:49:07,152
"Mozart"? Mozart is dead.
His troubles are over.

794
00:49:07,238 --> 00:49:09,147
Help <i>me!</i>

795
00:49:09,240 --> 00:49:12,157
[ Sighs ]
All right. I'm sorry.

796
00:49:12,243 --> 00:49:16,287
You're right. If you had to work,
you had to work.

797
00:49:16,371 --> 00:49:18,280
Oh, l-l-I love you too.

798
00:49:18,373 --> 00:49:21,540
Where is the guy's number?
The permit man.

799
00:49:21,626 --> 00:49:23,535
In the den, you think.

800
00:49:23,628 --> 00:49:26,035
I will pick you up
at the station.

801
00:49:26,130 --> 00:49:29,581
Just give me a call
when you get there. [ Kissing Sounds ]

802
00:49:42,520 --> 00:49:44,429
"Shrapp"?

803
00:49:56,783 --> 00:49:59,190
Is Mr Shrapp in?

804
00:49:59,285 --> 00:50:02,202
Mr Shrapp.
Walter Fielding.

805
00:50:02,288 --> 00:50:05,205
Hey, watch what you say
about my mother, now.

806
00:50:05,290 --> 00:50:07,413
Mr Shrapp,
let's be adults about this.

807
00:50:07,501 --> 00:50:10,751
I'm... Look, I'm very sorry
I wasn't here this afternoon.

808
00:50:10,837 --> 00:50:14,372
My wife was poisoned
and taken to the hospital.

809
00:50:14,465 --> 00:50:16,374
[ Taps Foot ]

810
00:50:16,467 --> 00:50:19,384
Well, what would
cut any ice with you?

811
00:50:19,470 --> 00:50:22,424
A bribe? Sure.
Can you be here in a half an hour?

812
00:50:23,807 --> 00:50:25,716
All right.

813
00:50:25,809 --> 00:50:27,718
Cash? No problem.

814
00:50:27,811 --> 00:50:29,933
[ Dial Tone ]

815
00:50:30,230 --> 00:50:31,937
Weasel.

816
00:50:32,023 --> 00:50:34,977
Cash.
Cash, cash, ca...

