00:52:04,398 --> 00:52:06,307
There!

846
00:52:06,400 --> 00:52:08,309
Nobody laughs
at Montgomery Shrapp!

847
00:52:11,196 --> 00:52:14,611
<i>[ Phone Ringing ]</i>

848
00:52:17,118 --> 00:52:19,573
<i>[ Ringing Continues ]</i>

849
00:53:06,787 --> 00:53:08,696
